caption.p: Effect of eucalyptus leaf and flower essential oils (EO) on different copulation parameters of C. maculatus F0 generation. ( a) F0 mating latency (s); ( b) F0 kicking phase start; ( c) F0 kicking duration (s); ( d) F0 copulation duration (s). There was no significant difference in the evaluated parameters ( P > 0.05).
